#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.80"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.80:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.80:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga"
msgstr "8. Guaranteed"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.80:0.3"
msgid "80. Kambojasutta"
msgstr "80. Persia"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.80:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "an4.80:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.83"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.80:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena mātugāmo neva sabhāyaṃ nisīdati, "
"na kammantaṃ payojeti, na kambojaṃ gacchatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why females don’t attend council "
"meetings, work for a living, or travel to Persia?”"

msgctxt "an4.80:2.2"
msgid "“Kodhano, ānanda, mātugāmo;"
msgstr "“Ānanda, females are angry,"

msgctxt "an4.80:2.3"
msgid "issukī, ānanda, mātugāmo;"
msgstr "jealous,"

msgctxt "an4.80:2.4"
msgid "maccharī, ānanda, mātugāmo;"
msgstr "mean,"

msgctxt "an4.80:2.5"
msgid "duppañño, ānanda, mātugāmo—"
msgstr "and unintelligent."

msgctxt "an4.80:2.6"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ kho, ānanda, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena mātugāmo neva sabhāyaṃ nisīdati, "
"na kammantaṃ payojeti, na kambojaṃ gacchatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why females don’t attend council "
"meetings, work for a living, or travel to Persia.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.80:2.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.80:2.8"
msgid "Apaṇṇakavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.80:3.1"
msgid "Padhānaṃ diṭṭhisappurisa,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.80:3.2"
msgid "Vadhukā dve ca honti aggāni;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.80:3.3"
msgid "Kusināraacinteyyā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.80:3.4"
msgid "Dakkhiṇā ca vaṇijjā kambojanti."
msgstr ""
